Title: Hiding something
Description: Save 1 harvest in your mouth until the end of the month. Can't be stolen from you and can't be dropped.

Title: Dashy Legs
Description: Add +2 dexterity when escaping from dog

Title: Houdini
Description: When failing to escape a trap, roll a dice, on a 4 to 6, ignore the trap penalty.

Title: Pink nose
Description: When you are on top a harvest with a poison token, you can pay 1 dexterity to flip the poison token face up

Title: Silky hands
Description: Steal 1 courage token from an animal standing next to you.
